<p>2
 The term &#8220;illicit&#8221; should not be conflated with &#8220;criminal&#8221; or &#8220;illegal&#8221;, although in the majority of 
</p>
<p>cases the funds in question will have been obtained in violation of domestic or international criminal 
laws. 
</p>
