</p>
<p>financing, monetary policy, financial reform and taxation as some of the areas that are essential for 
mobilizing resources. See also the report of the Special Rapporteur on the right to food on his mission 
to Brazil (A/HRC/13/33/Add.6, para. 36). 
</p>
